headline: Garmin and Noonan Collaborate to Bring Launch Monitor Data Seamlessly Onto the Course
summary: Garmin®, a global leader in GPS-enabled sports technology, and Noonan, a golf strategy app, today announced a new integration that allows Garmin Golf customers to seamlessly import their launch monitor data into Noonan's digital caddie platform.

headline: Flex Stock Up 75% in 12 Months: Will the Momentum Hold Amid Headwinds?
summary: Flex stock surges 75% in a year, fueled by data center expansion, strategic buys and broad advanced manufacturing strength.
